OL,3,COne man dead and 27 injured as British
OL,4,Ctourist bus crashes in Canary Islands
OL,6,FFootage released by local media shows
OL,7,Fthe bus lying on its side in a steep
OL,8,Fravine.
OL,10,FA British man has died and 27 others
OL,11,Fhave been injured after a bus carrying
OL,12,FBritish holidaymakers crashed in the
OL,13,FCanary Island of La Gomera, ITV News
OL,14,Funderstands.
OL,16,FEmergency services confirmed the death
OL,17,Fof the man. One person has been
OL,18,Fcritically injured and flown to a
OL,19,Fhospital on the nearby island of
OL,20,FTenerife for treatment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
