OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775931065
OL,3,COne man dead and 27 injured as British
OL,4,Ctourist bus crashes in Canary Islands
OL,6,FOne other person has also been
OL,7,Ftransferred to Tenerife, while the
OL,8,Frest of the injured have been taken to
OL,9,Fa hospital on La Gomera.
OL,11,FThe bus appears to have come off the
OL,12,Froad at a hairpin bend, ending up
OL,13,Flying on its side in a ravine.
OL,15,FThey said the bus was carrying 28
OL,16,Fpeople, 27 of whom were British
OL,17,Ftourists, and the other person was the
OL,18,Fbus driver.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
