OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775931065
OL,3,COne man dead and 27 injured as British
OL,4,Ctourist bus crashes in Canary Islands
OL,6,FPresident of La Gomera's Council
OL,7,FCasimiro Curbelo said the situation
OL,8,Fwas being closely monitored.
OL,10,FHe wrote on social media: "I thank the
OL,11,Frapid and coordinated response of the
OL,12,Fpersonnel involved in the operation".
OL,14,F"Regrettably, the death of one of the
OL,15,Foccupants has occurred, and we are
OL,16,Fclosely following the progress of the
OL,17,F27 injured individuals who are
OL,18,Freceiving medical attention at this
OL,19,Ftime."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
