OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1775931065
OL,3,COne man dead and 27 injured as British
OL,4,Ctourist bus crashes in Canary Islands
OL,6,FLocal authorities have declared a
OL,7,Fstate of alert due to the incident,
OL,8,Fwhich occurred at roughly 1:20 pm. A
OL,9,Fhelicopter ambulance, five ambulances,
OL,10,Fand a medical team have been deployed
OL,11,Fto the scene.
OL,13,FLa Gomera is the second smallest of
OL,14,Fthe eight major Spanish Canary
OL,15,FIslands. It is a ferry ride away from
OL,16,FTenerife, and often a day-trip
OL,17,Fdestination for tourists visiting the
OL,18,Fislands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
